{"tid":1158592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【肥得致命】560磅胖婦4年來首在協助下落床 痛得流淚終難逃大限","createTime":"2019-05-17T05:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T06:31:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b7858cedf8d6141745c2b364df683f0b362fd91d","tid":1158592,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"英國第五台（Channel Five）近日播放一套紀錄片，講述一名胖婦在2014年離世前的生活苦況。她的體重高達560磅，4年來從未試過下床。丈夫因為不想她整天臥床，於是訂造巨型梳化希望可一同在客廳看電視。不過胖婦下床時痛楚難當，終未能如願，她死前也只是坐過一次那張梳化。<br />\n住在西米德蘭茲（West Midlands）的58歲埃克爾斯頓（Denise Eccleston）本來是護士，後來因背傷要辭職，自此體重就一直暴增，7年來從未離開家門一步。埃克爾斯頓的脊椎情況太惡劣，導致胸口承受的壓力大增，要靠氧氣罩協助呼吸，她亦患上慢性淋巴水腫（lymphoedema），加劇全身痛楚。<br />\n丈夫為免她終日留在房內，特地花8,000鎊（約8萬港元）訂造一張超巨型單人梳化，讓兩人可一起在客廳看電視。埃克爾斯頓本想試坐，不過只是數步之遙的距離，對她來說可謂無比艱辛，丈夫及2名護理員要用病人起重機將她送上特製輪椅，再送她去客廳，僅移動1.2米卻用上半小時。<br />\n埃克爾斯頓痛得哭着乞求想留在床上，「這樣行不通，我做不到」，不過丈夫及護理員就一直安慰她。雖然成功將她帶離病床，但因為客廳的病人起重機故障，令埃克爾斯頓等人的努力付諸流水。<br />\n埃克爾斯頓表示：「我懷念過去可盡太太及母親義務的時光，我現在被困這間房內，根本出不去。我想保持樂觀，因為我是個樂觀的人。我兩周前也試過想離開病床，但我很痛楚，最後要找救護員協助。」在拍攝紀錄片期間，埃克爾斯頓仍希望，她和丈夫可以回復昔日的生活，但可惜最終未能如願。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190516/large/1557976115_92fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190516%2Flarge%2F1557976115_92fa.jpg&h=7356d375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190517/59605994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190517%2F59605994&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=4bbaad4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190517%2F59605994&h=3b7a600c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190517/59605994</a>"},{"pid":"eb155993478b7367586c64a167e0ecbdba60ae43","tid":1158592,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"點解可以肥到咁"},{"pid":"a9b99401fcd6e4932e89e15fe6bc7071d9b56509","tid":1158592,"uid":89801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"肥婆痛得要死"},{"pid":"e00030407288b6b886cf05f68d2887bfee65a80c","tid":1158592,"uid":89801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9b99401fcd6e4932e89e15fe6bc7071d9b56509","tid":1158592,"uid":89801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"肥婆痛得要死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"完全沒有心機"},{"pid":"128f990fb423410c967a460863f1f49ca3af278a","tid":1158592,"uid":68802,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"廢物黎<br />\n死左好呀"},{"pid":"280c287f7219e1fbefd2947d5fb8b0da24aed867","tid":1158592,"uid":229767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"辛苦又食咁多"},{"pid":"fc9396cde132b7ce10c7ff4547655118fa8c6a90","tid":1158592,"uid":34023,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9b99401fcd6e4932e89e15fe6bc7071d9b56509","tid":1158592,"uid":89801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"肥婆痛得要死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"屌好好笑"},{"pid":"1159acf81b500edcd13bd5b34d92ba64c51634e0","tid":1158592,"uid":60131,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e00030407288b6b886cf05f68d2887bfee65a80c","tid":1158592,"uid":89801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9b99401fcd6e4932e89e15fe6bc7071d9b56509","tid":1158592,"uid":89801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"肥婆痛得要死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"完全沒有心機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"碌出廳也不OK"},{"pid":"43d1138f9a3674625f875f0e90eea6d494664ba2","tid":1158592,"uid":46170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05: